  "description": "Product Description:\n\nDiscover the allure of cobalt spinel with this exquisitely crafted lab-grown cobalt spinel ring. This elegant piece features a stunning halo design set in high-quality S925 sterling silver, known for its hypoallergenic properties and long-lasting shine, making it perfect for daily wear.\n\nThe ring’s centerpiece is a captivating 6x8mm, 1.67-carat oval-cut lab-grown cobalt spinel that dazzles with its rich blue hue. Surrounding the main stone and gracefully adorning the band are luxurious round-cut accent stones, totaling 0.181 carats, adding an extra layer of sparkle and sophistication. Weighing 3.44 grams, this ring is available in U.S. sizes 5 to 7.5, with an estimated shipping time of 3-15 days for lab-grown colored gemstone rings.\n\nKey Features:\n\nLab-Grown Cobalt Spinel: A 6x8mm, 1.67-carat oval-cut stone with a striking blue color that’s both vibrant and elegant.\n\nHalo Design with Pavé Accents: A luxurious halo and band adorned with round-cut stones, enhancing the brilliance of the central gem.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver Setting: Crafted from hypoallergenic sterling silver, offering comfort and durability.\n\nAvailable Sizes: U.S. ring sizes 5 to 7.5 available.\n\nShipping: Lab-grown colored gemstone rings ship within 3-15 days.\n\nThis lab-grown cobalt spinel ring is a modern masterpiece, perfect for those who seek a unique, high-quality statement piece that embodies elegance and sophistication.",
